title: Stunning Townhome! WOW! CALL TODAY! MUST SEE!
posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'Welcome to 5347 Tennis Lane, a tastefully renovated 2bed/2bath villa, located in the gated, all-age community of Country Lake in Delray Beach!', 'This single story, corner home comes with an eat-in-kitchen with new shaker-style cabinetry, granite counters, designer tile backsplash, and newer SS appliances including a Samsung french door refrigerator.', 'Open and bright floor plan with porcelain, wood-look tile flooring throughout, designer light fixtures, new blinds, newer tankless water heater, smart thermostat, new impact glass windows, new roof, and Ring doorbell.', 'Spacious primary bedroom suite with a large walk-in closet with custom closet cabinets, and an en suite bath with a walk-in shower and a dual sink, designer vanity.', 'Generously-sized second bedroom', 'and a gorgeous second/guest bath with a walk-in shower w/pebble tile floor and designer accents.', 'Relax on the fully tiled, covered, and screened patio overlooking the large community lake.', 'There is an extra storage closet on the patio and a separate, open area for your BBQ.', 'Country Lake offers many amenities including a community pool, tennis courts, playground and much more.', 'Located close to Delray Medical Center, fun and exciting Downtown Delray, all major transportation, the beautiful Morikami Museum, and zoned for excellent Boca middle and high schools.', "Don't miss out-schedule your showing today!"]
